attributes.Long form description: The student gets the task of assembling the RASHULT rolling cart, so he starts by aligning the middle tray with the sidebars and assembling the bars in order to get the whole sidebar. Then the student aligns the bottom tray with the sidebars and screws it using the bolts and the hex nuts into the sidebars. And then he does the same with the middle tray and the top tray. The student tightens all the bolts and hex nuts of the trays using the wrench and then the student continues to assemble the first, second, third and fourth rotary wheel into the base frame.
